title: [Requiell's Magic Shoppe]
[Requiell's General Store]
[Requiell's Outfitting]
description: A bundle of dried flowers hangs on one of the refined oak-paneled walls, and a viridian Vornavian silk ceiling rises overhead.  A plush black bear fur rug sits in one corner of a varnished dark oak floor.  There is a heavy white granite counter on one side of the shop.
